OL,3,C'Million-to-one' chance baby survived
OL,4,Cdrinking drain unblocker
OL,6,FThe parents of a baby from Birmingham
OL,7,Fwho drank drain unblocker were told it
OL,8,Fwas a "million-to-one" chance that he
OL,9,Fsurvived.
OL,11,FSam Anwar, from Highgate, was just 13
OL,12,Fmonths old when he crept up behind his
OL,13,Fmum, who was cleaning the bathroom at
OL,14,Ftheir flat, and drank caustic soda
OL,15,Ffrom a white bottle.
OL,17,FHe suffered burns to his mouth,
OL,18,Ftongue, lips and airways. After
OL,19,Fsuffering a heart attack, he was
OL,20,Funconscious for three minutes.
