OL,6,FHis father, Nadeem Alshameri, 37, said
OL,7,Fhe will require a complicated
OL,8,Foperation to "unlock" his mouth and
OL,9,Frepair the damage caused from the
OL,10,Fburns inside.
OL,12,FSam had surgery, but will require
OL,13,Ffurther operations.JThe dad-of-four
OL,14,Fhas set up a fundraising page to help
OL,15,Fpay for any medical bills.
OL,17,FHe said doctors continue to disagree
OL,18,Fabout the best way to treat his son,
OL,19,Fleaving the family to explore
OL,20,Fspecialist medical options abroad.
