OL,4,Cdrinking drain unblocker
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old warehouse worker said:
OL,7,F"The Mrs was cleaning in the bathroom
OL,8,Fand he had been playing with his
OL,9,Fsiblings and toys in the living room.
OL,11,F"Within a few seconds, he had popped
OL,12,Fin the bathroom as we live in a flat.
OL,13,FHe came behind her and she didn't
OL,14,Frealise he was behind her and saw the
OL,15,Fcaustic soda on the floor, which is to
OL,16,Funblock the drains/sink.
