OL,3,C'Million-to-one' chance baby survived
OL,4,Cdrinking drain unblocker
OL,6,F"He grabbed it and thought it was a
OL,7,Fbottle of milk and started drinking
OL,8,Fit. The taps were on (didn't hear him
OL,9,Fcome in), and she didn't have time to
OL,10,Fget to him.
OL,12,F"The GP said it was one in a million
OL,13,Fhe survived. It's killer stuff. He
OL,14,Fpassed out for three minutes and had a
OL,15,Fheart attack. It's a miracle he
OL,16,Fsurvived and came back to life."
OL,18,F"I've been told they will try and do
OL,19,Fan operation for him.
