OL,3,C'Million-to-one' chance baby survived
OL,4,Cdrinking drain unblocker
OL,6,F"Some doctors said they will do the
OL,7,Fsurgery, but others say it's too early
OL,8,Fto do. They don't know what to do with
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F"We could try and take him away to be
OL,12,Ftreated abroad. But we don't have
OL,13,Fenough money to do that.
OL,15,F"We worry about him putting things
OL,16,Finto his mouth because he can't
OL,17,Fswallow and will start choking. I'm
OL,18,Fworried about him every day."
